{
  "stem": "22869.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Where, all of a sudden, you lose your-- your whole dignity.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "First of all, just to perform an act of going to the bathroom in front of other people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't have to mention to you what it is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, if it's done en masse, men and women, in the same-- no, excuse me-- there were only men, at this time-- in-- in one place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was-- it was an awful, an awful sight, and an awful experience.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It really-- By the time we arrived to Lublin, we like thanked to God to have a little-- little fresh air, there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they gave us these special shoes-- wood shoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I forgot-- they have a name for them, but I forgot the name.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They're made in Holland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What are they called?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Clogs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a shoe in which you can walk-- barely walk-- but you can never run.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, when they unloaded us in Lublin [INAUDIBLE], in Lublin, they had us put these shoes on, because they were scared somebody will run away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had us march to the Majdanek camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no recollection of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just, like, so thankful to have a little fresh air again, to breathe, and to be a little bit free of movement and so, that I-- I can't recall anymore any other thing that sits in my mind.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were SS there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were SS and dogs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I have to tell you this-- that the reception in Zilina was much worse than the unloading right now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was bad, but it wasn't as bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they did a lot of-- that belonged probably to their way of dealing with people, to try to dehumanize you-- yelling, screaming, dogs barking.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
